title: Precious Undoing
description: Precious Undoing by Autumn WinchesterPain. That was all I once knew. Now, free from the clutches of Alan, I’m struggling to stand on my own two feet. I don’t know who I am, or where I stand with my new family. Can I become the brave person everyone says I am? Or will my depression take full control over my slow discovery of hope?
author: Autumn Winchester
